{"id":"3b191a48-a65c-4e6b-9554-9a3ac4b035b7","name":"Cairo - Season Two","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>\"The desert sun has clearly cooked your brain until you’ve begun hallucinating a throne for yourself.\"</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/skhey1MFaQOZXCaZh6ezE.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6jBRN88Xv24C-QfdYALLM.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong><em><u>T</u></em></strong><em><u>oday's Noble</u>..</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\"><strong><em>Two years of peace, alliances and everything going well.. But the peace is breaking, again.</em></strong></p><p class=\"is-empty\">​Cairo is a king who carved his crown out of the same silk that once bound him as a captured concubine. He is a man who won't hesitate to kill for peace, a ruler who trusts no one and suspects everyone. To the world, he is an impenetrable fortress and cruelty. But even a fortress has a master key.</p><p class=\"is-empty\"><em>And that key is </em><strong><em>you</em></strong><em>.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty\">Cairo trusts no one. He fears nothing. And he certainly doesn’t believe in ghosts, especially not a \"king\" named Kamal who claims to rule a kingdom that isn't on any map.</p><p class=\"is-empty\">​Cairo is a king who was once a slave. He is a lover who was once a weapon. And if anyone dares to step between him and his husband, they will learn that the desert isn't the only thing that knows how to make a man vanish.</p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/y4pdfJ9Kd_ZqIuyvSh3NH.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"div Btn2-purple pp-pg-total\" href=\"https://forms.gle/fgmLm8xUhJuTeWj87\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(139, 18, 18);\"><strong>Submit your pet</strong></span></a></p><p></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u>Extras</u></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WFeyuluXCSYreSYEyG-V3.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/NaL2XAXFrT0p-NyVS20o8.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/cR-XEbO3DeWmxZ3ldr9bL.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/F75_EP6FXBqcSj7fi_GAd.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_MmVF2lTBMdEzniM2-Ps_.webp\" style=\"width: 276.773px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br></p><hr><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 23px;\"><strong>⚠️ Content Warnings </strong></span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><em>Possible m𝖾𝗇𝗍𝗂𝗈𝗇𝗌 𝗈𝖿&nbsp;</em><strong><em> (all this is the past but MIGHT happen again) death/murder, enslavement, war/violence, dubious consent, possessive behaviour, kidnapping.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6jBRN88Xv24C-QfdYALLM.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong><em><u>K</u></em></strong><em><u>oFi</u></em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LLQ0RaPC0ReyxHnL3jDdh.webp\" style=\"width: 293.648px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p 